AND MEMPHIS, TENNESSEE. APPAREL AND EQUIPMENT PRODUCTS ARE SHIPPED FROM OUR MEMPHIS, TENNESSEE, TIGARD, OREGON, AND FOOTHILL RANCH, CALIFORNIA DISTRIBUTION CENTERS. COLE HAAN PRODUCTS ARE DISTRIBUTED PRIMARILY FROM GREENLAND, NEW HAMPSHIRE, CONVERSE

