CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS AND (2) THE EFFECTIVENESS OF OUR INTERNAL CONTROL OVER FINANCIAL REPORTING AS OF MAY 31, 2008, AS STATED IN THEIR REPORT HEREIN.

