FASB STATEMENT NO. 115 (FAS 159). FAS 159 PERMITS ENTITIES TO CHOOSE TO MEASURE MANY FINANCIAL INSTRUMENTS AND CERTAIN OTHER ITEMS AT FAIR VALUE. THE PROVISIONS OF

