ACTIVITIES BY REQUIRING ENHANCED DISCLOSURES TO ENABLE INVESTORS TO BETTER UNDERSTAND THEIR EFFECTS ON AN ENTITYS FINANCIAL POSITION, FINANCIAL PERFORMANCE, AND CASH FLOWS. THE PROVISIONS OF FAS 161 ARE EFFECTIVE FOR THE QUARTER ENDING

